% CITATION NOTES:
% ============================================
% 1. Always include DOI when available
% 2. Use proper capitalization for titles
% 3. Include all authors (use "et al." in citation, not in bibliography)
% 4. For Chinese references, include langid={chinese}
% 5. Use consistent formatting for similar reference types
% 6. Include URLs and access dates for online resources
% 7. Use software for statistical software and programming languages
% 8. Use dataset for data sources
% 9. Use curly braces {} to preserve capitalization in titles
% 10. Use \& for "and" in author lists (BibTeX handles this automatically)